title: Windows XP GERMAN barebone edition (no service packs)

GERMAN GERMAN GERMAN GERMAN GERMAN GERMAN GERMAN GERMAN GERMAN GERMAN GERMAN GERMAN

NO SERVICE PACKS!!!

Some nice Austrian friends told me that it&#039;s no problem, and made me a copy of their XP CD, which was unfortunately in German. I don&#039;t need a German version but if you do, here it is. I zipped it with winrar, but in ZIP format.



DON&#039;T ASK ME FOR A CRACK OR SERIAL NUMBER!



I simply don&#039;t have a German serial number.

This is for people who&#039;s CD got just as fucked up as mine.
